en_544241_0	An awareness lecture to educate school children, parents and teachers on explosives was conducted at Madduma Bandra Kanishta Vidyalaya at Pilimathalawa on Friday (7).
en_544241_1	This valuable lecture was delivered on the directions of the Commander, Security Forces - Central, Major General Laksiri Waduge and under the supervision of the General Officer Commanding 11 Division.
en_544241_2	Captain R.M.I Bandara of the 11 Division conducted this session and alerted the public on security measures and how they should act in an emergency.
